  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a clinical randomized controlled study.The objective of this study is to&#xD;
      compare the prognosis of patients with ARDS between eit-v / q-oriented individualized&#xD;
      ventilation strategy and traditional lung protection ventilation strategy, and to establish&#xD;
      the demonstration application of eit-v / q-oriented ventilation strategy in ARDS&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
